snippet.title: Grapplers: Relic Rivals - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Grapplers: Relic Rivals is out now on PC!  Dodge deadly traps, utilize your grappling hook, and master each relic to defeat your opponents and reign victorious in this thrilling PvP platformer!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2906890/Grapplers_Relic_Rivals/

Art by Nicolas Pava (https://twitter.com/SeinRuhe)
Sound design by Lukas Raymond (https://www.lukasraymond.com/)
Game design by Paul Kankiewicz (https://paulkankiewicz.com/about/)

#IndieGame #GameTrailers #Gaming

"Retro Game Music Pack - Level 1" by Juhani Junkala (SubspaceAudio), used under CC0 1.0
"Victory" by celestialghost8, used under CC0 1.0
